review_text: First, let me say that I discovered this product quite by accident. I used to use prescription sleeping pills to help me sleep because of my disruptive travel schedule. I track my sleep using an app on my smart watch. I could see the difference almost from day one. I sleep longer and have better quality sleep when I do. Keep in mind this product will not be able to overcome lots of afternoon caffeine drinking, but it will help you feel more rested and sleep better when you do.

review_text: I consider "Nightrest" a miracle supplement in my life.
